#The state of having a small distance from one terminating point on an object or an area to another terminating point.  Short can apply to [[horizontal]] or [[vertical]] dimensions.
#*Short in the positive [[vertical]] dimension is usually said [[Short]], but short in the negative vertical dimension is referred to as [[Shallow]].

==Synonyms==
[[Short]], [[Low]], [[Narrow]], [[Slim]], [[Shallow]]

==Antonyms==
[[Tall]], [[High]], [[Wide]], [[Broad]], [[Deep]]